title: Algeria Consumer Spending
description: Consumer Spending in Algeria increased to 9645101.80 DZD Million in 2021 from 8684553.40 DZD Million in 2020. Consumer Spending in Algeria averaged 4300277.05 DZD Million from 1995 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 9645101.80 DZD Million in 2021 and a record low of 1103081.90 DZD Million in 1995. This page provides - Algeria Consumer Spending - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Office National des Statistiques (ONS)
